{"tid":814785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港樓顛價大灣區買樓增　80後：怕老了在港沒地方住","createTime":"2018-09-11T13:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T14:49:10.000Z","uid":82845,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aab3652ccf487d9c524accffadf7d6da9d67492c","tid":814785,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2155000/2157161/001_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2155000%2F2157161%2F001_1024.jpg&h=2ad5741b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港樓價高，加上大灣區概念落實，不少港人北望神州買樓，有地產代理稱80後年輕人到大灣區買樓投資增，已佔港客三分一。另有地產代理指，<span style=\"color: red;\">隨着高鐵通車，深圳北站的樓盤查詢上升</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有80後港青3年前看好內地房地產升值潛力，獨沽一味投資有港珠澳大橋及中深通道概念的中山區，<span style=\"color: red;\">至今持有20套房，市值逾2,000萬元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥早前在一個論壇致辭時表示，大灣區可為港人追求更美好生活，提供廣闊腹地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">80後港人陳小姐2016年以約40萬</span>元人民幣在惠州購買一個酒店房間作投資之用，其後她又擔心香港樓價太高，老了在香港沒地方住，兩年後再以約30萬人民幣在惠州購買一個二手住宅單位，<span style=\"color: red;\">她認為惠州在大灣區內發展一定比香港好</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2155000/2157161/copy20180830026_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2155000%2F2157161%2Fcopy20180830026_1024.jpg&h=3a174118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同是80後的阿鋒，比陳小姐更早投身內地樓市，<span style=\"color: red;\">3年前在中山買下首個物業，之後不斷投資，至今已擁有20個舖或住宅單位，市值逾2,000萬人民幣。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨着大灣區的發展，他正計劃將所有本港物業放售，以換取更多資金在中山炒樓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以係大灣區買樓真係冇死錯人,呢位80後就有眼光啦! 抵佢發<br />\n你地成班連登仔冇父幹就留係度同新移民搶公屋啦,爭到既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要學人買新樓,有會所,又冇錢,父幹又冇乜都冇,舊又睇唔上眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓天橋底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2157161/%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E9%A1%9B%E5%83%B9%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E5%A2%9E%E3%80%8080%E5%BE%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%80%95%E8%80%81%E4%BA%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%B2%92%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E4%BD%8F?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2157161%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%25A1%259B%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A2%259E%25E3%2580%258080%25E5%25BE%258C%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2580%2595%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BD%258F%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=7oWBNXCUekGj5IX4dWOr3AHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=756a9ee2\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2157161/%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E9%A1%9B%E5%83%B9%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E5%A2%9E%E3%80%8080%E5%BE%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%80%95%E8%80%81%E4%BA%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%B2%92%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E4%BD%8F?r=cpsdlc</a>"},{"pid":"33dc48352169af929ade4d72e6579a695303c1c4","tid":814785,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"作新聞？"},{"pid":"b2ad57c39b5edcc568bb2675d1e843b3ae011991","tid":814785,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0